column1: # This file was produced by the NASA Exoplanet Archive  http://exoplanetarchive.ipac.caltech.edu
# COLUMN kepid:          KepID
# COLUMN kepoi_name:     KOI Name
# COLUMN fpp_koi_period: KOI Transit Period [days]
# COLUMN fpp_prad:       Planet Radius Value [Earth radii]
# COLUMN fpp_prob:       Probability to be Any of the Considered Astrophysical False Positive Scenarios
# COLUMN fpp_score:      Sum of Likelihood for All of the Considered Models (DR24) or Shape Score (DR25)
# COLUMN fpp_delivname:  Name of Delivery
# COLUMN fpp_spec_occrate: Specific Planet Occurrence Rate
# COLUMN fpp_secthresh:  Maximum Allowed Secondary Eclipse Depth [ppm]
# COLUMN fpp_maxrad:     Maximum Allowed Sky-Projected Distance for False Positive [arcsec]
# COLUMN fpp_prob_heb:   Probability to be a Hierarchical Eclipsing Binary
# COLUMN fpp_prob_ueb:   Probability to be an Unblended Eclipsing Binary
# COLUMN fpp_prob_beb:   Probability to be a Blended Eclipsing Binary
# COLUMN fpp_prob_heb_dbl: Probability to be a Double Period Hierarchical Eclipsing Binary
# COLUMN fpp_prob_ueb_dbl: Probability to be a Double Period Unblended Eclipsing Binary
# COLUMN fpp_prob_beb_dbl: Probability to be a Double Period Blended Eclipsing Binary

# COLUMN fpp_slogg:      Stellar Surface Gravity [log10(cm/s**2)]

# COLUMN fpp_smet:       Stellar Metallicity [dex]

# COLUMN fpp_srad:       Stellar Radius [Solar radii]
# COLUMN fpp_srad_err1:  Stellar Radius Upper Unc. [Solar radii]
# COLUMN fpp_srad_err2:  Stellar Radius Lower Unc. [Solar radii]
# COLUMN fpp_smass:      Stellar Mass [Solar mass]
# COLUMN fpp_smass_err1: Stellar Mass Upper Unc. [Solar mass]
# COLUMN fpp_smass_err2: Stellar Mass Lower Unc. [Solar mass]
# COLUMN fpp_sage:       Stellar Age [Gyr]
# COLUMN fpp_sage_err1:  Stellar Age Upper Unc. [Gyr]
# COLUMN fpp_sage_err2:  Stellar Age Lower Unc. [Gyr]
# COLUMN fpp_dist:       Distance [pc]
# COLUMN fpp_dist_err1:  Distance Upper Unc. [pc]
# COLUMN fpp_dist_err2:  Distance Lower Unc. [pc]
# COLUMN fpp_av:         Av Extinction [mag]
# COLUMN fpp_av_err1:    Av Extinction Upper Unc. [mag]
# COLUMN fpp_av_err2:    Av Extinction Lower Unc. [mag]
# COLUMN fpp_max_av:     Maximum Allowed Av Extinction [mag]
# COLUMN fpp_pr_steff_mu: Prior Stellar Effective Temperature Mean [K]
# COLUMN fpp_pr_steff_sig: Prior Stellar Effective Temperature Standard Deviation [K]
# COLUMN fpp_pr_slogg_mu: Prior Stellar Surface Gravity Mean [log10(cm/s**2)]
